explanations.description: Various forms of the prefix "hom-" which can express different meanings such as similarity (homolog, homage, homophobic), home (homestead, homeschool, homepage), and more, or just forms of the word "home" (homicide, homeschooling, homemaker) and lastly, words ending in -er (homer).
